### 40.1 Offline Detection

**Triggers**:
- Browser `offline` event
- Failed network requests (3 consecutive failures)
- Server unreachable (timeout after 30s)

**Status Indicator**: Yellow banner below TopBar

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
