- Background: #FFB300 @ 10%
- Border-bottom: 2px #FFB300 @ 20%
- Text: 15pt Body, #B36A00 (dark orange)
- Button: Secondary style, inline
- Dismissible: ✕ icon, but reappears on next screen

### 40.2 Feature Availability Matrix

| Feature | Online | Offline |
|---------|--------|---------|
| Dashboard | ✅ Full | ⚠️ Cached (shows timestamp) |
| Access Control | ✅ Full | ❌ Disabled (real-time required) |
| Members - View | ✅ Full | ✅ Cached list |
| Members - Add/Edit | ✅ Full | 🔄 Queued (syncs when online) |
| Registrations | ✅ Full | ⚠️ Cached (can't approve offline) |
| History | ✅ Full | ⚠️ Cached (last 7 days) |
| Finance | ✅ Full | ⚠️ Cached data |
| Staff | ✅ Full | ⚠️ View only |
| Shop - View | ✅ Full | ✅ Cached catalog |
| Shop - Edit | ✅ Full | 🔄 Queued |
| Settings | ✅ Full | ✅ Local settings work |
| Search | ✅ Full | ✅ Searches cache only |

**Legend**:
- ✅ Full: Works normally
- ⚠️ Cached: Shows stale data with warning
- 🔄 Queued: Actions queued for sync
- ❌ Disabled: Feature unavailable

### 40.3 Offline Queue System

**Queued Actions Stored Locally**:
- Add member
- Edit member
- Delete member (soft delete)
- Add/edit product
- Update inventory
- Change settings

**Queue UI Indicator**:

```
┌──────────────────────┐
│ 🔄 3 changes pending │
└──────────────────────┘
```

- Position: Floating bottom-right, 24px from edges
- Height: 48px, auto width
- Background: #FFB300 @ 90%
- Text: 14pt Medium, #FFFFFF
- Shadow: Level 2
- Click: Opens queue details modal

### 40.4 Queue Details Modal

**Dimensions**: 640px width, auto height

**Structure**:
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Pending Changes                              [✕]    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ ➕ Add Member: John Doe                         │ │
│ │    2m ago • Waiting for connection              │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ ✏️ Edit Product: Protein Powder                 │ │
│ │    5m ago • Waiting for connection              │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ These changes will sync automatically when you're   │
│ back online.          [Retry Now] [Discard All]    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Queue Item**:
- Icon: Action type (➕ ✏️ 🗑️)
- Title: 17pt Body Medium, #1A1A1A
- Subtitle: 14pt Caption, #999999
- Timestamp: Relative ("2m ago")

### 40.5 Sync Process

**When Connection Restored**:

1. Toast: "🔄 Syncing pending changes..."
2. Process queue sequentially
3. For each item:
   - Attempt sync
   - **Success**: Remove from queue, update cache
   - **Conflict**: Show conflict resolution modal
   - **Error**: Increment retry counter, keep in queue
4. When complete:
   - Toast: "✓ All changes synced"
   - Refresh affected screens
   - Full data sync (pull latest from server)

### 40.6 Conflict Resolution Modal

**Scenario**: User edited member offline, but member was also edited online

**Modal** (640px width):
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Conflict Detected                            [✕]    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ This member was modified while you were offline.    │
│                                                     │
│ Your Changes          Server Version               │
│ ┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐          │
│ │ Name: John Doe  │  │ Name: John Doe  │          │
│ │ Phone: 555-0123 │  │ Phone: 555-9999 │ ← Diff   │
│ │ Email: john@... │  │ Email: john@... │          │
│ └─────────────────┘  └─────────────────┘          │
│                                                     │
│ [Keep Mine] [Use Server] [Merge Manually]          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Actions**:
- **Keep Mine**: Overwrite server with local changes
- **Use Server**: Discard local, use server version
- **Merge Manually**: Opens edit form with both versions visible side-by-side

### 40.7 Cached Data Management

**What's Cached** (IndexedDB):
- Members: Max 1000 most recent
- Products: Max 500 active products
- Access events: Last 7 days only (max 500)
- Notifications: Last 100

**Cache Expiration**:
- Access events: 7 days
- Notifications: 30 days
- Members/Products: Never (unless manually deleted)

**Manual Cache Clear**:
- Settings > Advanced > "Clear Cache" button
- Confirmation: "This will delete all offline data"
- After clear: Force full sync on next connection

