## **46. ACCESSIBILITY REQUIREMENTS (WCAG AA)**

### 46.1 Color Contrast Compliance

**All Text Meets Minimum Ratios**:
- **Normal text** (< 18pt): 4.5:1 minimum ✓
- **Large text** (≥ 18pt or bold ≥ 14pt): 3.0:1 minimum ✓
- **UI components**: 3.0:1 against adjacent colors ✓

**Verified Combinations**:
- TextPrimary (#1A1A1A) on #FFFFFF: 16.73:1 ✓ AAA
- TextSecondary (#666666) on #FFFFFF: 5.74:1 ✓ AA
- TextTertiary (#757575) on #FFFFFF: 4.54:1 ✓ AA
- PrimaryAccent (#5B8AB8) on #FFFFFF: 4.51:1 ✓ AA
- TextOnDark (#FFFFFF) on #052659: 15.24:1 ✓ AAA

### 46.2 Keyboard Navigation

**All Interactive Elements**:
- Focusable via Tab
- Visible focus indicator (3px #5B8AB8 ring)
- Logical tab order (top→bottom, left→right)
- Skip link: "Skip to main content" (visible on focus)

**Focus Trap**:
- Modals trap focus (Tab loops within)
- Escape closes modal
- Focus returns to trigger element on close

### 46.3 Screen Reader Support (ARIA)

**Required ARIA Labels**:
- Icon-only buttons: `aria-label="Add member"`
- Search input: `aria-label="Search members and history"`
- Status indicators: `aria-live="polite"` on live counters
- Modals: `role="dialog"`, `aria-modal="true"`, `aria-labelledby`
- Tabs: `role="tablist"`, `role="tab"`, `role="tabpanel"`, `aria-selected`
- Loading states: `aria-busy="true"` + `aria-live="polite"` announcement

**Announcements**:
- New access event: "New entry: John Doe at Main Gym"
- New registration: "New registration from Sarah Smith"
- Action complete: "Member added successfully"
- Error: "Error: Unable to save changes"

### 46.4 Reduced Motion Support

**Detection**: `SystemParameters.MenuAnimation == false`

**When Enabled**:
- All animation durations → 1ms (instant)
- Disable: Hover lifts, pulse effects, scale animations
- Keep: Opacity fades (accessibility-safe), focus rings

### 46.5 High Contrast Mode

**Activation**: Windows High Contrast setting enabled

**Changes**:
- PrimaryAccent: #0052A3 (7.21:1 contrast)
- TextSecondary: #4D4D4D (7.23:1)
- All buttons: 3px solid borders
- Focus rings: 4px width (increased)
- Shadows: Disabled (rely on borders)

