Columns:
- FacilityFeatureID (PK)
- FacilityID (FK to Facilities)
- FeatureName (ENUM: HasMembers, HasAccessControl, HasProducts, HasServices, HasOrders, etc.)
- IsEnabled (BIT)
- Configuration (NVARCHAR(MAX), JSON, nullable)

Indexes:
- Clustered index on FacilityFeatureID
- Non-clustered index on (FacilityID, FeatureName) for fast lookups
TimeSlots Table Design:
Columns:
- TimeSlotID (PK)
- FacilityID (FK to Facilities, for Hammam/Pool only)
- DayOfWeek (TINYINT: 0-6)
- StartTime (TIME)
- EndTime (TIME)
- Gender (ENUM: Male, Female)
- IsActive (BIT)
- RecurrenceType (ENUM: Weekly, OneTime)
- SpecificDate (DATE, nullable, for one-time slots)

Indexes:
- Non-clustered on (FacilityID, DayOfWeek, StartTime)
- Check constraint: EndTime > StartTime

